Does anyone else think this is BS? I have completed a few of the Wizard quests outta Temple of Solusek (Acumen Mask and Runescale Cloak especially), and find it a bit messed up that Verant decided to make Wizards be the only class that HAS to do their own quests (yes, yes, they can be tag teamed, but still...)<br>
<br>
Acumen Mask and Runescale cloak are NODROP items when the quests are completed. Cleric Quest Armor, Warrior Armor, Bard Armor, Enchanter Gear, Pally Armor, Shaman Armor, ...All DROPPABLE... (I can't comment on the Mage or Necro gear, never messed with that..)<br>
<br>
WTF is the deal? Its not like the components for the quests are droppable...So WHY is the final result NODROP?<br>
<br>
Has anyone ever commented on this on Whineplay? (I seldom go there...) If so, did Wizards just get the standard response about it being a &quot;Game Balance Issue&quot; and part of the &quot;Vision&quot;??? Is it worth trying to even bring this up?<br>
